data.description: Don't miss out on this gem! Nestled on 1 acre, serene location without HOA restrictions, this captivating property boasts 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. The master suite conveniently occupies the main floor, complemented by a charming rocking chair front porch and a spacious covered porch. Enjoy year-round comfort in the Florida room, complete with a cozy wood stove. Step out onto the screened porch for additional relaxation. With ample space for outdoor activities, the expansive grounds are perfect for children to indulge in games. Upstairs, you'll find generously sized secondary rooms adding to the allure of this wonderful home.
